      "side": 1,
      "message": "bigtable can store multiple values for a key, each differentiated by a timestamp. So instead of doing this you can just use the id as they key and set the row timestamp from msg.Timestamp.\n\nJust make sure you don\u0027t set garbage collection on this table.",
      "revId": "c232da1e628e6935c9eef1e4fcd8fbc910bc3b58",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
